cov-lineages/pangolin-data.name: pangolin-data v1.32
cov-lineages/pangolin-data.body: Release of pangolin-data repository corresponding to [pango-designation version 1.32](https://github.com/cov-lineages/pango-designation/releases/tag/v1.32).  This repository is compatible with pangolin v4.3 onwards.

nextstrain/nextclade_data.name: 2025-03-26--11-47-13Z
nextstrain/nextclade_data.body:
This release contains changes for datasets:

- SARS-CoV-2 (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/wuhan-hu-1/orfs)
- SARS-CoV-2 (Mature proteins) (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/wuhan-hu-1/proteins)
- SARS-CoV-2 (BA.2) (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/BA.2)
- SARS-CoV-2 (XBB) (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/XBB)
- SARS-CoV-2 (BA.2.86) (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/BA.2.86)
- Influenza A H1N1pdm NA (nextstrain/flu/h1n1pdm/na/MW626056)
- Influenza B Victoria NA (nextstrain/flu/vic/na/CY073894)
- Mpox virus (Clade I) (nextstrain/mpox/clade-i)
- Measles N450 (WHO-2012) (nextstrain/measles/N450/WHO-2012)
- Yellow fever virus (YFV) prM-E region (nextstrain/yellow-fever/prM-E)
- PRRSV-1 (community/isuvdl/mazeller/prrsv1/orf5/yimim2025)
- PRRSV-2 ORF5 Lineages, Yim-im & Zhang 2023 Microbiol Spectr (community/isuvdl/mazeller/prrsv2/orf5/yimim2023)
- DENV-1 (community/v-gen-lab/dengue/denv1)
- DENV-2 (community/v-gen-lab/dengue/denv2)
- DENV-3 (community/v-gen-lab/dengue/denv3)
- DENV-4 (community/v-gen-lab/dengue/denv4)
- Orthomarburgvirus marburgense (community/genspectrum/marburg/HK1980/all-lineages)
